    <!-- Section: What works -->
    <section id="what-works">
      <h2>What works today — practical tools</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>3D imaging & simulation</strong> — standardized capture increases consult clarity and conversion. (Example: VECTRA / 3dMD)</li>
        <li><strong>Intra-op analytics (blood-loss)</strong> — objective, real-time estimations support safer decisions (Triton by Gauss/Stryker).</li>
        <li><strong>Remote wound triage</strong> — AI-assisted photo triage flags problems early; reduces unnecessary visits (Swift Medical).</li>
        <li><strong>Administrative automation</strong> — speech-to-text, ambient scribing and scheduling reduce clinician time on admin tasks.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="muted">Learn more: <a class="link" href="https://www.srinjoysaha.com/ai-in-surgery">srinjoysaha.com/ai-in-surgery</a></p>

      <!-- SVG image placeholder -->
