    <!-- Section: Benefits -->
    <section id="benefits">
      <h2>Clinical benefits — why adopt</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Clearer patient communication — visual simulations align expectations.</li>
        <li>Earlier detection of complications — better safety and fewer readmissions.</li>
        <li>Time savings for clinicians — outsourcing documentation and routine triage.</li>
        <li>Actionable outcomes data — objective metrics to refine technique and quality improvement.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="muted">For scar management resources see: <a class="link" href="https://www.srinjoysaha.com/scar-management">srinjoysaha.com/scar-management</a></p>

      <svg class="svg-divider" viewBox="0 0 800 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <rect width="800" height="60" fill="#fff7ed"></rect>
